The Bismarck is a WW2 German Battleship officially launched in February 14, 1939. Its fate would soon follow as it was sunk in May 1941. 


I hope you guys like this project if you do, make sure to, Like, Favorite, and Subscribe for more! 
俾斯麦是在1939年2月14日德国正式推出的二战战列舰。它的命运结束在1941年.
